on the new controls in iOS 14.


551
00:28:37,284 --> 00:28:41,655 line:0
Those new controls are gonna work great
in your iPadOS and your Mac Catalyst apps


552
00:28:41,722 --> 00:28:43,257 line:0
in addition to on the iPhone.


553
00:28:43,957 --> 00:28:47,628 line:0
You can also go deeper in how to build
all of these features into your apps


554
00:28:47,694 --> 00:28:49,663 line:0
with the session "Build For iPad."


555
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:52,833 line:0
It'll show you how to use all of these
from within your code.


556
